    </header>
    <div itemprop="text" class="entry-content">
      <img align="left" itemprop="image" class="entry-author-image" src="//0.gravatar.com/avatar/b56bb22b3a4b83c6b534b4c114671380?s=50">
      <p>Written by Google Developer Expert (GDE) Todd Motto, this Angular tutorial serves as an ultimate resource for learning AngularJS.</p>
