      </span>
    </p>

  </footer>
</article>
<article itemprop="blogPost" itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting" itemscope="itemscope">
  <a rel="bookmark" target="_self" title="The Top 10 Mistakes AngularJS Developers Make" href="/angularjs/posts/top-10-mistakes-angularjs-developers-make">
    <header class="entry-header">
      <h2 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">The Top 10 Mistakes AngularJS Developers Make</h2>
      <p class="entry-meta">
        <time datetime="2014-10-01T22:02:35.113Z" itemprop="datePublished" class="entry-time"></time>
